Both exhibit the symmetry
under the replacement , which corresponds to replacing quarks
by anti-quarks. Moreover,
both expressions imply  that  at 
_k = k _1,
where  is the tension of the fundamental string (i.e. ).
The difference is in the subleading in  corrections.
In the first case they run in powers of  while in the second
in powers of .

The purpose of this paper is two-fold. First, we will 
argue(Strictly speaking the
